---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="Help — Should I Go Outside?"
  description="How Should I Go Outside? works, our approach to privacy, and how to get in touch."
>
  <main class="page">
    <div class="card">
      <a href="/" class="back-btn">← Back to home</a>

      <h1 class="heading">Help</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Here's everything you need to know about Should I Go Outside?
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-heading">What is Should I Go Outside?</h2>
        <p>
          Should I Go Outside? is a simple app that checks the weather where
          you are and tells you whether it's worth going outside. It looks at
          temperature, rain, wind, and more, then gives you a clear yes or no.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-heading">How it works</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Open the app.</strong> No sign-ups, no accounts, no setup.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Share your location.</strong> The app uses it to check
            weather conditions near you.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Get your answer.</strong> A quick recommendation on whether
            to head out or stay in.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Your privacy matters</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>We don't track you.</strong> Your location is used once to
            fetch weather data, then it's gone. We never store it.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>We don't share your data.</strong> No selling, no renting,
            no trading.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>No accounts, no profiles.</strong> There's nothing to store,
            so there's nothing to breach.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Want the full details? Check out our <a href="/privacy" class="link"
            >Privacy Policy</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Need more help?</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions or run into issues, send us an email at
          <a href="mailto:contact@toebeans.life" class="link"
            >contact@toebeans.life</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="footer-note">
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">← Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .card {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-outline);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-offset-lg) var(--shadow-offset-lg) 0 0
      var(--color-shadow);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
    max-width: 720px;
    width: 100%;
    transform: rotate(-0.5deg);
  }

  .back-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-outline);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-offset) var(--shadow-offset) 0 0
      var(--color-shadow);
    transition:
      transform 0.15s ease,
      box-shadow 0.15s ease;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .back-btn:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 0 var(--color-shadow);
  }

  .back-btn:active {
    transform: translate(1px, 1px);
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 0 var(--color-shadow);
  }

  .back-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .heading {
    font-family: "Lexend Mega", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding-bottom: 1.75rem;
    border-bottom: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-outline);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: "Lexend Mega", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  ul li {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  ul li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-coral);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .link {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-primary);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: text-decoration-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .link:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-coral);
  }

  .link:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    outline-offset: 2px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .footer-note {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.75rem;
    border-top: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-outline);
  }

  .footer-note .back-btn {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page {
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem;
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .back-btn,
    .link {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
